{"word":"Assyria","slug":"assyria","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Assyria</b> <a href=\"#/H804\">H804</a> <br/> An empire founded by Nimrod<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=10&verse=12'>Gen 10:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=5&verse=6'>Mic 5:6</a> <br/> - It extended from east of the Tigris<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=2&verse=14'>Gen 2:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=10&verse=11'>Gen 10:11</a> <br/> - It extended possibly to Egypt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=18'>Gen 25:18</a> <br/> - Its armies invade the land of Israel under:<br/> b Pul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=15&verse=19'>2Ki 15:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=26'>1Ch 5:26</a><br/> b Tiglath<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=15&verse=29'>2Ki 15:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=6'>1Ch 5:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=26'>1Ch 5:26</a><br/> b Shalmaneser<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=17&verse=6'>2Ki 17:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=17&verse=27'>2Ki 17:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=18&verse=12'>2Ki 18:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=50&verse=17'>Jer 50:17</a><br/> b Sennacherib<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=18&verse=37'>2Ki 18:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=19'>2Ki 19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=32'>2Ch 32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=36'>Isa 36</a><br/> Army of:<br/> - Destroyed by the angel of the Lord<br/> <a href='https://www.wo